channel.title: Can someone really help me with this error plleaaase?
channel.description: I've had this error for as long as i can remember and that's what stopped me from continuing making runescape private servers, but now i want to get back into the servers and i still have this error. When i run my server it says "Error: Unable to startup listener on 5555 - port already in use?". I know i have to open it or something but i just don't know much about this, so if anyone can help me it would be much appreciated.

item.title: Can someone really help me with this error plleaaase?
item.dc:creator: @Slave_Scyth Slave Scyth
item.description:
@Slave_Scyth wrote:

Open up a Command Prompt, type “netstat -b -a”

Look through the results, looking for ‘5555’. Go into task manager and kill the process of the program using port 5555.

EDIT: Always quicker than me, jc. Lol
